    MANAGERS --> MODELS
    
    MIDDLEWARE --> API_VIEWS
    MIDDLEWARE --> SERVICES_BACKEND
    
    TASKS --> SERVICES_BACKEND
    TASKS --> MODELS
    
    WEBSOCKET --> SERVICES_BACKEND
    WEBSOCKET --> MODELS

    %% External Connections
    MODELS -->|"Read/Write"| PostgreSQL
